{"he6f0e1b7gcd39g4de3g8aa6ga44a7c7d4595": ["...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "a11ccad4-2105-2250-9a58-b34ffcb77d8b"], "h70738de8g10b3g4c2egbb5cg2e8951917668": ["Go to Hell.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "5a3a1432-3725-2bb1-d95d-be4472b6a94f"], "hfd3ad252g1e9bg427fgb409g56895c74e6c8": ["And good evening to you too.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "6d4c1351-3e01-bc16-8d95-d7b2ba833987"], "h97f73edfg07afg486egb89bg3860d7c8d36d": ["Hah. You're a good sport.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "206aa89c-6ecf-4381-3f57-135e9fe943da"], "h3416fb59gcbdbg471cga5a3g89d52539e6d2": ["'Go to Hell.' An everyday expression. So trivial it's almost meaningless.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "23f3f0eb-c169-0f36-7f97-d35944952da2"], "hc0b2af74g13dcg4caag8270g067d1d17b935": ["But we've seen Hell. It's real. And it isn't trivial.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "71690556-7b77-c2b2-e09f-e8769716ec55"], "h53835e15g0a39g4686g925eg68a3b6759155": ["What's on your mind, Gale?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "c696b70f-968d-b83a-5d08-f2aad7105b98"], "h1fff78e6g99f8g46acgb6feg70f2ee8dd419": ["Devils, dragons, mind flayers - they used to be abstracts. Pictures on a piece of paper.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "573f80a0-a7c9-2440-def7-78ef26e4f599"], "h76d55357gbf1eg4c90g986agaeef625d0f3f": ["What a difference a day makes.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "164bed16-fa2f-b902-e584-5429d6d33602"], "h8de0ce14gb265g4ebag91a5gc10206dbc39f": ["Now we have tadpoles slithering through our heads like carnivorous foeti.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "d546c878-61f4-3a48-d71f-bd196e25aa74"], "h4b11c674g9f8eg4e5fgac68g3e13d1010577": ["That's not abstract.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "72e7bf5a-60e9-bbbd-31ff-6617bb79ff0e"], "h2fc59379ged81g4fb4g83c8g32cc6411bb0c": ["I'm not too worried. We'll find someone who can help us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "e00464c0-0784-1aaf-c9b2-dc8eeeaca55a"], "hc6b50e42g9f74g46fdga023g14cc99da32d4": ["That's the spirit. Let's be up with the lark - find a healer before the wee one gets hungry.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "6eee3ae9-beb0-4803-f771-2f40bcd303ca"], "ha7e23481ge461g481cgaabfgf7b3f1f3d540": ["Perhaps you should get some rest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "315c97aa-9f7a-c4e5-0dc4-1c9c2e610752"], "h7664e9dag8349g4f36ga869g15655c66858b": ["This ballet of flames invites reflection. But you're right.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "39dfd3c7-3b80-7a37-b864-d658543eba22"], "h8bd2a659gfd5fg411bg9f77g999ee7178127": ["Let's be up with the lark - find a healer before the wee one gets hungry.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "8340762f-82ba-1608-f024-54de30ae97f5"], "hac6f35c1g4a41g40a9gb330gca042d0821a7": ["Brooding will get us nowhere. Action will.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "c0d02e2f-0e8e-b8c4-d872-2ccc726f5e7d"], "h5ae1be7dga59ag4dacga190g40f58154b5aa": ["What can I say but that you're right? We're in deep you-know-what.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "5a6bdd40-32f0-aabc-8346-9d5d05223169"], "hd658e09fg794eg4612g932agda3fe43005b6": ["Point well-made, I see.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "945587d4-6540-96e1-0548-4c110f797aa7"], "ha10b3c8egd8aag45c1gaab3g720509f17c73": ["I'll wake you bright and early. We'll need to find a healer before the wee one gets hungry.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "616fe9ff-7528-9d9d-befc-f67fa20ecc98"], "h0af15dcagd34cg43b7g9b26g1cd701693a50": ["<i>Watch the flames in silence.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "a7d5bc98-9c0c-618c-8b51-ac64f155cc29"], "hd0acde12gb3e1g49e9g8001gcdebe7fe8c09": ["You sound a tad more dejected than when we first met.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "274d8a78-8504-ec2b-e1a5-569c28351c07"], "h11d8873ag5223g47d4gba25g4140edec7630": ["Merely contemplating.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "7220ec0e-4fc8-38be-f021-33cd282f1487"], "hb1ca98deg01a6g49dfg90fdgfb817f2a3c54": ["Was there anything in particular I did to deserve such a greeting?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "338e7cf8-2e8d-c7a5-d285-9aa3294c993a"], "h1263c580g798fg4956gb8adg39073086dc9a": ["Oh. Nothing, nothing. I'm just poorly making a point.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "071ceaac-735e-54cc-610d-0f485b814c78"], "h5d4f4e8egd374g4f37g9556ge5dc3a84b67e": ["Watch your damn mouth!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "6da3e9dd-19bc-ee36-b5a9-df8edcf2c6d7"], "h29929bc8g1b3eg48ddg9716ga23a1067be6c": ["Hold your horses! I'm just poorly making a point.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Gale.html", "975da3ab-294c-dfb0-e6b2-152992d8e997"]}